<paragraph id="45A412E023203D98B2A0423198CDB27B" pageId="41" pageNumber="72">Type locality. Black Sea, at Feodosiya and Adler (Crimea, Ukraine).</paragraph>
<paragraph id="D4F7F3ADE07FF935754D932F18B86F6D" pageId="41" pageNumber="72">Distribution. Black Sea Basin; northern Aegean Sea; Lake Sarikum, Turkey; northern Adriatic Sea.</paragraph>
